title: InfinityNest - Dragon Nest Private Server -
description:
Site: https://infinitynest.com/

Experience
The amount of EXP you get from hunting monsters is fixed, meaning you can run any dungeon at any difficulty and you will still receive the same amount of Experience.

We suggest that you run dungeons like the Astral Coven Laboratory (ACL/DTMI) until level 50. After that you could run Queen's Garden in Liverwort Marina until level 60. For more in-depth information, refer to this guide.

Gold
We have slightly increased gold rates although there's few good ways to farm gold.

The most efficient way to gain gold is to run abyss dungeons and sell the Dimensional Fragments. If you want more information about gold farming, you can refer to this guide.

Drop
The drop rates are slightly increased, just like the gold rates, however it's very easy to farm in-game.

For example, if you run a nest or two, you can gain enough materials to craft an entire Lvl. 60 Epic gear set! Altheums and diamonds to enhance your gears are easy to drop as well.
Enhancement
100% success rate for Lvl. 60 Epic gear until +8. After that, the rates are roughly same as in official server
